    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is clean and retains a nice shine, though it shows minor signs of use including a few small stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches near the door handles. Inside, the cabin is tidy and smoke-free, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a complete service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
