    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for the discerning driver. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical excellence and long-term reliability. With its sophisticated profile and robust performance capabilities, this offering provides a superior balance of luxury and value, ready for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-loved\u2014runs like a dream and the interior is still looking great and feeling cozy. If you're looking for a reliable car that\u2019s been properly cared for and is ready for many more adventures, this is the one! I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out and come take a look!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery through its individual throttle bodies and high-revving valvetrain. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain remains tight with a factory-spec limited-slip differential providing excellent corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its communicative feedback, benefiting from recent suspension bushing refreshes and a documented rear subframe inspection. Mechanically sound with a clean VANOS operation and consistent oil analysis results, this M3 represents a balanced example ready for the B-roads. Cosmetically honest with minor patina consistent with spirited use, it\u2019s a turn-key performance icon for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Reliable daily driver. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Engine runs strong. Maintenance up to date.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, reflective gloss, having been frequently waxed and kept in a climate-controlled garage. While there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel\u2014standard for its mileage\u2014the body is straight and free of any major dents or rust. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the dashboard is free of any cracks or sun damage. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and heated seats, is in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth power, backed by a complete service log showing oil changes every 5,000 miles. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes were serviced just last season. This is a non-smoker vehicle, carries no pet odors, and comes with two original key fobs and all factory manuals. It is a reliable, turn-key car ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated design. This unit offers reliable performance and a refined driving experience, having undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for quality and safety. An exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a premier balance of prestige and value.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
